---
description: Shared workflow rules for all tasks
globs: **/*
alwaysApply: true
---

## Workflow
- Follow Discuss -> Plan -> Slice -> Execute -> Verify -> Ship.
- Plan before editing on non-trivial tasks.
- Prefer vertical slices.

## Evidence
- Never claim success without checks.
- End with summary, evidence, risks, rollback.

## Safety
- Do not overwrite workflow files blindly.
- Do not commit secrets.
- Do not change deploy config without explicit scope.
